{"tid":221493,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"從個樣, 係睇出你既習慣","createTime":"2017-04-28T17:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T06:15:33.000Z","uid":89064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c146bf3bd483eb1b48d2213dfe9515b8745ee1a","tid":221493,"uid":89064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"後生食煙可能唔覺。 <br />\n其實食煙食耐左, 人地一睇你個樣就知道你有食煙。<br />\n<br />\n食左例如5-10年既人, 望落去塊面係一係又黃又黑又厚, 一係咀唇會好深色, 冇左原來好有血氣既鮮紅色。同埋如果係多年長期食煙, 飲酒, 望落去有種江湖中人既感覺。<br />\n以上呢d可觀特徵係冇得呃人。<br />\n<br />\n冇食煙既人個樣, 差極都有個譜, 就算係40,50歲既人, 望落去個樣都清新, 精神, 咀唇面色紅潤。"},{"pid":"5241b4eac8c381abb43883f2514943aec4380d03","tid":221493,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:40:46.000Z","msg":"食左6-7年煙 一日一包，個樣殘左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e904a159a2b57fe32860762f924b648f5db204","tid":221493,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左6-7年煙 一日一包，個樣殘左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食左2年, 個樣同2年前對比, 真係少咁左果種純淨, 有朝氣既氣色, 我決定要戒煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3689e6b27fbc361756ea7e3585d704397bf06298","tid":221493,"uid":55637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食左6-7年煙 一日一包，個樣殘左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食左2年, 個樣同2年前對比, 真係少咁左果種純淨, 有朝氣既氣色, 我決定要戒煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講左好多次戒但次次都收皮<br />\n因為返工成日想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2063d3d4cd549ee7aa442b84cb9a23081a50cdd0","tid":221493,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食左6-7年煙 一日一包，個樣殘左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食左2年, 個樣同2年前對比, 真係少咁左果種純淨, 有朝氣既氣色, 我決定要戒煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講左好多次戒但次次都收皮<br />\n因為返工成日想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我而家通常2日一包, 因為而家番緊學, 諗諗下都係張買煙既錢儲起黎, 買自己鐘意既野好似波衫波褲仲好, 一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35326a828d27a324f25b3083e533aa6232d5f4e","tid":221493,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T23:42:46.000Z","msg":"做運動就知咩事"},{"pid":"c5a1f4caba5f8315cd72d9d5c92060bbf8cd13b5","tid":221493,"uid":56160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"江湖中人既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f1146b4cf8d95a8df35eaed2aaa5e39ccac46b","tid":221493,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左6-7年煙 一日一包，個樣殘左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}